      "span_text": "Because CD11b/c labels all macrophages, CD11b ϩ cells in a control experiment were incubated in anti-CD11b/c-PE and anti-CD45-FITC (BD Biosciences Pharmingen) to determine the relative concentration of perivascular macrophages, which label as CD11b ϩ /CD45 high  ."
